overview: The 5th annual Smash Wrestling CANUSA Classic is set for December 3rd in Toronto and tickets are on sale now. Here's what we know so far. Allie will remain as captain for Team USA and Rosemary will not be captaining Team Canada this year. For the first time in CANUSA history, Canadian wrestling legend Gail Kim will appear on the show. She'll take on Allie in the main event of the evening.
title: Smash CANUSA Classic
